{
  "stem": "1826.2",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 13.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "You can only say it was a miracle, if somebody is religious.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "You can say whatever you want.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Anyway, she didn't see me.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And she didn't hear me.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And these two German gendarmes-- they couldn't-- they didn't find me.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They didn't find anything.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then they had to make a report.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then I hear one says to the other, in German, [SPEAKING GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It means, in English, take a look.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "How much grain is in the sack?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They had to put it in the report.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So he comes in, into the barn, with a flashlight.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I was lying on the floor, next to the grain.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I hear him.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "He says, [GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And somehow, he didn't see me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "He didn't-- He.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Didn't see me.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "What was going through your mind?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then, when the gendarmes left, I went.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And [?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Maria ?] [?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Nikichna ?] kissed me, and said-- and said, Grisha, you are under the protection of the Holy Spirit.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "This-- this was it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But this place was already compromised, shall we say, correct, you know?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So I couldn't continue to stay there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The other man was taken-- he went-- somebody took him to go to another town, [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The name of it was [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I was the only one.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But I can tell is that Maria [?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Nikichna ?] had one chicken.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And since I looked so bad, she killed the chicken for me, to feed me.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So I was [INAUDIBLE] what for to do now, what to do.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Then I said-- the next night, I slept.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "There were some strawberries, or other, you know, in the-- in the outdoors.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And it was November.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "It was already cold, it was.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I [? sat through ?] there.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
